54
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:28,300
Not easy as all that.

55
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:31,380
Get an eyeful of the lady.

56
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:54,100
She may have pinched it herself... What's her name?

57
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:57,340
Alice Roberts, most often.

58
00:07:57,460 --> 00:08:00,420
Yes, she may have appropriated the microfilm.

59
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:04,020
You'll worm it out of her.

60
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:07,820
She looks pretty beastly, eh?

61
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:11,410
Uncommonly pretty beastly!

62
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:14,730
How shall I contact her? - You'll find her at the hotel bar.

63
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:18,420
You'll address her: ""Shall we dance?""

64
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:21,500
And she'll answer: ""As soon as I finish my brandy.""

65
